{"tid":1463173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[短文] 癱瘓機場之我見 求集思廣益","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:23:15.000Z","uid":131527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee63d7cfeba07c132ffc706809c153302ce7055f","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"一直都係做cd rom/ 覆po推po 但對癱瘓機場有感而發<br />\n<br />\n 我就好撚支持癱瘓機場作壓逼手段 和平遊行無撚用大家都知 但勇武抗爭硬碰都係唔明朗 面對港共政府 警黑合作 (屌你老母呀殺人兇手) 同最關鍵既<span style=\"color: red;\">武力嚴重差距</span> 呢兩個月我地已經損傷左太多手足 <br />\n<br />\n我地下一條出路 就係<span style=\"color: red;\">搞鳩佢d錢</span> 一直都覺得香港比到大陸既野就係錢 (大白象既利益輸送 每日派蝗黎分薄我地既福利)<br />\n<br />\n反抗佢既人命根本分文不值 唔可以再遵從道德去理解一個極權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得運動進入以癱瘓機場直線打擊經濟既階段<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人數</span></span>係我地最大既優勢<br />\n<br />\n人數黎講 一定係和理非既天下 經過琴日 我地發現原來塞爆機場佢係會跪低<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非手足們 機場係暫時唯一用和平手段可以逼使港共正視我地訴求既地方 所以出到一定要出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係邊個唔洗搵食 現實地將代價降低先可以令更多人出黎 琴日市民憤怒達至頂點 我身邊唔少人都真係罷工出去 但持久度一定係低 都係今日人數直線下降既原因<br />\n<br />\n機場最過癮既位就係全天候運作 每一刻都唔停得 我提議先由大部分人得閒既日子 <br />\n比如 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每逢星期五六既夜晚就入去參觀</span></span> 去重演琴晚既劇本 會係打爆機場既一個出路 <br />\n<br />\n另外講少少分化問題<br />\n<br />\n今日好多人屌鳩勇武手足不智 但係以琴日為例 後面成千上萬人頂住前線手足邊個會想亂衝勇武 而結果最後係湊效只係對面用資源優勢(狗+民航+交通+網軍) 吹左一鼓好強既散水風嚇怕和理非 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次有用比你拋到 下次呢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日人少無得揀 前線想做更多野出左阻遊客呢個方法去癱機場 比唔心急既和理非指責都係意料中事 但並唔應該咁做 只會不斷分裂 削弱己方實力 一齊搵個共識先係正途<br />\n<br />\n希望可以一齊討論 減少分化 謝<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"11c2023b586d418af675e6a0ddafb703c852ad9c","tid":1463173,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"有貨運巴打講過 <br />\n<br />\n星期六 晚 係直接處理 星期日+星期一既貨運<br />\n<br />\n換個講法 極度需要人"},{"pid":"7a36c08e0e7b39877c80b8995e7e0329d1e8810c","tid":1463173,"uid":71919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"平日好難有琴日咁多人<br />\n如果星期六/日再搞一次<br />\n一黎大家有時間 一黎有時間做文宣<br />\n平日可以繼續接機 散播訊息"},{"pid":"4842c96f323f105ee14dcfa90036000ce7aaee68","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c2023b586d418af675e6a0ddafb703c852ad9c","tid":1463173,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"有貨運巴打講過 <br />\n<br />\n星期六 晚 係直接處理 星期日+星期一既貨運<br />\n<br />\n換個講法 極度需要人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"咁絕對係一個好消息<br />\n<br />\n相比起平日 星期六晚 or even 全日既時間對大部分人都係休息時間 奉獻呢d時間會總廉價過平日番工既日子吧 要人多就要現實入手"},{"pid":"bbfdfc7d6a2ddf5690934310144e15adca5ffa9b","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a36c08e0e7b39877c80b8995e7e0329d1e8810c","tid":1463173,"uid":71919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"平日好難有琴日咁多人<br />\n如果星期六/日再搞一次<br />\n一黎大家有時間 一黎有時間做文宣<br />\n平日可以繼續接機 散播訊息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"琴日既人多主要係前日班狗癲到將港人對濫暴團火都點著番 但總會熄"},{"pid":"feb73af4ad6ee9313c1c5e9fdcae0787751ed4bb","tid":1463173,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"逢五六參觀機場有得諗<br />\n亦同意今次比較衝動"},{"pid":"826fb5653f20fb63ca5b2a2caa49a4e7a5dd0b5d","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb73af4ad6ee9313c1c5e9fdcae0787751ed4bb","tid":1463173,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"逢五六參觀機場有得諗<br />\n亦同意今次比較衝動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"始終時間成本每個人唔同 我地目的要瘋狂聚集人"},{"pid":"8bcc6b2efa875accab3fc4d4e4d6465f13f1f406","tid":1463173,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"同埋要有足夠文宣先好實行一個活動<br />\n<br />\nBetween明明係長文做咩話短文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54c2bfdc2616ce75d269fe6ff9ec1444a544833","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bcc6b2efa875accab3fc4d4e4d6465f13f1f406","tid":1463173,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"同埋要有足夠文宣先好實行一個活動<br />\n<br />\nBetween明明係長文做咩話短文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"同意既 固定某d日子黎做都有個好處係長期運作到 文宣負擔都會細d <br />\n<br />\n呢排興標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb51406486153ba2e13f028cda1af78a8ecf9b9f","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbc1c3a3726412aa5a3733ad1ca38e460cb7f5e0","tid":1463173,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效，而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋靠民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"dfc9ce2ffe9959c33d2b895352e1ef8da4f66680","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc1c3a3726412aa5a3733ad1ca38e460cb7f5e0","tid":1463173,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效，而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋靠民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"住何威脅到政權既方法都要試 就係部分和理非手足未接受到既野 亦都係不分化既一大難度 <br />\n<br />\n琴日係兩個月黎和理非行動第一次壓逼到極權既大日子 突然間今日就用一個相對粗暴咁多既方法 實會有不滿 <br />\n<br />\n我地要解釋上晝人少都好都要撼動個政權比影響力 其實係勇武行為既體現 大家目的都係一樣 <br />\n<br />\n無人寫包單夜晚會多人 無謂因爲道德光環失去太多行動力"},{"pid":"3e01a08e1efa6b42ba1486b00dd7c2c0b1147e31","tid":1463173,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb73af4ad6ee9313c1c5e9fdcae0787751ed4bb","tid":1463173,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"逢五六參觀機場有得諗<br />\n亦同意今次比較衝動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係"},{"pid":"2b49975346f68c303e9929ba1bd14f325d077168","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d1e50c3ed5e59b1557abadaee5f86c5652ea0070","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"214beab0fd2b54f326929e44d44f323a12a99e47","tid":1463173,"uid":131527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGhdLuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGhdLuH.jpg&h=c7cc1c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場係我地唯一出路 唔想再見到手足獨自承受街頭抗爭既代價"},{"pid":"38bcc782e714772815a5965d7efb64413453c844","tid":1463173,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}